{
  "stem": "23626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- right away in the morning and at night-- every second night I stayed on to serve for the company he was entertaining.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was almost up every night, almost every night he would-- he would even sometimes just drink all night, if he wouldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to be there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As long-- as long he didn't go to bed, I had to be on duty.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One of us have to be on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And many times, if he didn't sleep all night, he would get up like very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It could be like, before 6:00, before people went to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is when he went out killing, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just-- just-- just like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, he-- he was-- he was not sleeping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He would get up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, he was-- he had a couple of different hats, you know, hanging right near the entrance of the-- of the-- of the villa.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you know, it's amazing that I knew what hat he would put on that he would be killing people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's how attuned I was to this wild animal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He would go early in the morning, like it must have been like, quarter to 6:00.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he would shot on the random.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the time, I knew that he did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because when he came through the gate of the villa, he would whistle, like a happy whistle, like-- like I felt he's content.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He accomplished something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then he went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It's very hard for me to talk about, especially about the time that I was with Goeth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] since we moved to the villa, I wasn't allowed to go to the camp anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
